## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture the most recent changes in healthcare policies across Europe. Additionally, the complexity and diversity of healthcare systems mean that some nuances may not be fully addressed. Further research, including interviews with healthcare professionals and policymakers, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of universal health care in Europe.